{"tid":1064123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿維他奶津貼厚此薄彼　員工集體請病假抗議","createTime":"2019-03-16T09:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T11:32:32.000Z","uid":191633,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"70bd13c4d21b628e0de3da328fc6c0dc92b5ccde","tid":1064123,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:56:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315184141462-0315_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190315184141462-0315_00822_001.html&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=91185e13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/mobile/bkn-20190315184141462-0315_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n維他奶屯門廠房爆勞資糾紛，員工集體請病假以示不滿。有自稱是該廠房的員工向東網報料，今日(15日)有約100名生產線早更員工參與行動，不滿資方在去年11月起向原料部員工提供每日60港元額外津貼，但生產部欠奉。維他奶職工會總幹事陳子傑表示知悉事件，正向參與行動的員工了解。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據知現時屯門廠房約有600至700名員工，主要來自生產部及原料部。陳正向發起工業行動的工友了解，又指以每日60港元計算，一個月可額外獲得津貼約1500港元，生產部員工薪酬一直偏低，平日要靠超時工作才能勉強過活，故早對資方厚此薄彼心存不滿，又估計行動已暫停大半生產線。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n維他奶承認今有少數員工請病假，但未有提供實際人數，重申屯門廠房的生產線運作及產品供應如常。該公司又指，就員工的整體薪酬待遇作檢討，參考經營環境及業界情況，考慮因素包括工作性質、資歷及勞工市場情況等，冀能確保員工的薪酬待遇具市場競爭力，資方本周與員工溝通，解釋相關修訂內容。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"90d76d7ebc8b2413e21e344a9edb59dee944c391","tid":1064123,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔：不了 要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c45c804e94a505aa55e4672a0049e9366951439","tid":1064123,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"到最後個解決方案係一鑊熟直頭取消埋個津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2840d62dbc662ecfe27fa641cdfcf03d71ffc1","tid":1064123,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:04:10.000Z","msg":"再噪，搬返哂返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664a69ed56a6b16d075ac5750fd8c2154b9a30d9","tid":1064123,"uid":228963,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:06:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85f45e1c136340da85d44bda2156a3e11a4e9bbc","tid":1064123,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ef1398c7e08460b55a6729f23378bedb4e4b541","tid":1064123,"uid":191633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5c45c804e94a505aa55e4672a0049e9366951439","tid":1064123,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"到最後個解決方案係一鑊熟直頭取消埋個津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"魚蛋論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eec2755c94e5559005d92604fa5fceb1c4c92e","tid":1064123,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"85f45e1c136340da85d44bda2156a3e11a4e9bbc","tid":1064123,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:10:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:14:40.000Z","msg":"禾地中國人最唔怕舌底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c5e3988451b069a676cea742e64439d13f9e6f","tid":1064123,"uid":53588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:15:40.000Z","msg":"12粒鐘1更 做6日。。。<br />\n人工又唔高 果時做左幾日頂唔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed223a40aa9f9a317f2edc757b87585a8a7d1f5e","tid":1064123,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:16:17.000Z","msg":"琴日九巴app 廣告就係維他奶請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0991be82ad423463af9ecea7595db983fd28777","tid":1064123,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46c5e3988451b069a676cea742e64439d13f9e6f","tid":1064123,"uid